{"tid":2344804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★傅聰----父母於文革時慘遭紅衛兵迫害身亡","createTime":"2020-12-29T04:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T06:19:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6894ff5111704e05ecd07381728b5f5e6e01489a","tid":2344804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"傅聰的父親是中國知名翻譯家傅雷，雖然其著作《傅雷家書》在如今的中國被稱為「父母聖經」，但傅雷夫妻其實下場悽慘，兩人在文革期間被打成「右派份子」，慘遭迫害身亡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1950年代末，傅聰因為父母慘遭文革批鬥，他逃離波蘭，開始長居英國倫敦。<br />\n傅聰的父親傅雷是留學法國的著名翻譯家，其翻譯作品多以社會弊端及人物奮鬥抗爭為主。在文革期間，傅雷夫婦被上海中共高層歸類成「右派份子」，慘遭紅衛兵日夜批鬥，夫婦兩人最後在家中自縊身亡。據說傅聰收到父親的最後遺言是：「第一做人，第二做藝術家，第三做音樂家，最後才是鋼琴家。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201229/GIO4G35GMNE3FIARZ56LY3OD4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201229%2FGIO4G35GMNE3FIARZ56LY3OD4U%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=7c1b1b6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201229%2FGIO4G35GMNE3FIARZ56LY3OD4U%2F&h=a5c7712a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201229/GIO4G35GMNE3FIARZ56LY3OD4U/</a>"},{"pid":"9384a99f550ec3a6609e0444993a32b61e2d7039","tid":2344804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ebe3a9c0b71ac677906399fc372e83c255075d","tid":2344804,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKOaKP